name: columbia
description: This International Women’s Day, it’s time to get outside. We’re celebrating women who scout bold new paths and wander long-loved routes. Women who look up, to where the same sky stretches above us all, and say “yes” to its wide open invitation to adventure, joy, and wonder. Now, it’s time to explore your outdoors. All sky. No limits.
img_alt: This International Women’s Day, it’s time to get outside. We’re celebrating women who scout bold new paths and wander long-loved routes. Women who look up, to where the same sky stretches above us all, and say “yes” to its wide open invitation to adventure, joy, and wonder. Now, it’s time to explore your outdoors. All sky. No limits.  A big round of applause for the fearless outdoorswomen from across the globe who shared their passion, insight, and voices with us: Cindy “Sid” Nguyen (USA), Sarah Hoefflin  (Switzerland), Nelly Attar (Lebannon / Saudi Arabia), Anna Laura (Brazil), Yoojung Shin (Korea), Arika Itoh (Japan), GirlTrek (USA), and Yurie (Japan). #iwd #internationalwomensday  created by Columbia Sportswear with Columbia Sportswear's original sound

name: columbia
description: Today we say “Happy Birthday” to our late founder Gert Boyle, a woman who never had trouble speaking her mind or forging her own path.
img_alt: Today we say “Happy Birthday” to our late founder Gert Boyle, a woman who never had trouble speaking her mind or forging her own path.  In 1970, stay at home mother of three, Gert took over Columbia Sportswear after the death of her husband. She quickly received an offer to sell her struggling family business for a mere $1,400. Gert turned down the offer and instead, cultivated Columbia into a global success; a company steadfast in the belief that the outdoors are for everyone.  This International Women’s Day, be like Gert. All sky. No limits.  created by Columbia Sportswear with Columbia Sportswear's original sound
